ZH: 1. 我们只是在这里过境，不会停留。
EN: We are just passing through here and won't stay.

ZH: 2. 在这个城市过境时，我们遇到了一场暴风雨。
EN: We encountered a storm when passing through this city.

ZH: 3. 机场是我们去目的地之前的必经之路。
EN: The airport is a transit point before reaching our destination.

ZH: 4. 他们只是在这里过境，所以没有时间参观周围的景点。
EN: They are just passing through here, so they don't have time to visit the surrounding attractions.

ZH: 5. 船只在这个港口停留了几个小时，然后继续向前航行。
EN: The ship stopped at this port for a few hours and then continued to sail.

ZH: 6. 我们的飞机延误了，因此过境的时间比预计的要长。
EN: Our flight was delayed, so the transit time is longer than expected.

ZH: 7. 马车带着旅客穿过森林，前往另一个村庄。
EN: The carriage carried passengers through the forest to another village.

ZH: 8. 这辆火车是我们去往旅游胜地的必经之路。
EN: This train is the transit route to the tourist destination.

ZH: 9. 因为交通事故，我们被迫绕道而行。
EN: Due to a traffic accident, we were forced to take a detour.

ZH: 10. 在过境的途中，我们享受了美丽的风景。
EN: We enjoyed the beautiful scenery on the way through the transit.

ZH: 11. 过境国的海关要对旅行者的行李进行检查。
EN: The customs of the transit country need to inspect the luggage of travelers.

ZH: 12. 飞机在机场过境时，工作人员会为乘客安排转机手续。
EN: When the plane transits at the airport, the staff will arrange the transfer procedures for passengers.

ZH: 13. 我们需要在这个城市过境一天，然后再继续旅行。
EN: We need to transit in this city for a day before continuing the journey.

ZH: 14. 这个国家不允许旅行者在过境时参加任何活动。
EN: This country does not allow travelers to participate in any activities during transit.

ZH: 15. 你们的大巴会在这个小镇过境吗？
EN: Will your bus transit through this small town?

ZH: 16. 在火车站过境时，记得拿好你的行李。
EN: Remember to take your luggage with you when transiting at the train station.

ZH: 17. 他们只是途经这个小岛，没有打算在那里停留。
EN: They are just passing through this island and have no intention of staying there.

ZH: 18. 过境的航班通常会提供免费的餐食和机场服务。
EN: Transit flights usually provide free meals and airport services.

ZH: 19. 在过境国境时，要遵守当地的法律和规定。
EN: When transiting at the border, you must comply with local laws and regulations.

ZH: 20. 他们到达过境点时，才意识到他们的护照被遗失了。
EN: They realized that their passports were lost when they arrived at the transit point.
